<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Dear investors,<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I hope this mail find you well.=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">This is our first mail to you a=
s investors in our fund after the final closing. &nbsp;We will highly appre=
ciate your feedback regarding the format and the information provided in or=
der to improve our future reports.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please find attached following =
documents:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 =
lfo3"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Executive Summary of Q2 2021 activity<o:p></o:p>=
</span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-lis=
t:l0 level1 lfo3"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Financial Statements of Q2 2021 (rev=
iewed by Deloitte)<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" sty=
le=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Capital=
 Call Notice<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">The fund appointed <b>Tzur Mana=
gement</b> as the administrator of the fund. For any questions please do no=
t hesitate to contact
</span><a href=3D"mailto:investorservices@tzurmanagement.com"><span lang=3D=
"EN-US">investorservices@tzurmanagement.com</span></a><span lang=3D"EN-US">=
.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">In addition, we were requested =
to provide an investors' list to the fund&#8217;s anchor institutional inve=
stor, please let us know if you have any reservations in this respect.</spa=
n><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif"><=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Shana Tova and Chag Sameach (Ha=
ppy Jewish New Year)!</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Aviran &amp; Danny</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
